1.10
log
@Use sigaction() instead of signal() to avoid pulling in unnecessary
wrappers.  To keep uses from crawling back in, mark signal() as
deprecated inside libc.

ok deraadt@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: signal.c,v 1.9 2015/10/23 04:39:24 guenther Exp $ */
